## Tools & Collaboration

- **Version Control & Repository:** GitHub  
  Used for source code management, documentation, and artifact storage.

- **Project Management:** GitHub Projects  
  Used to manage the product backlog, track Product Backlog Items (PBIs), and support sprint planning and progress tracking.

- **UI/UX Design & Prototyping:** Figma  
  Selected due to team proficiency and its support for collaborative wireframing and prototyping.

- **Team Communication:** Microsoft Teams  
  Used for team discussions, coordination, and synchronous or asynchronous Scrum ceremonies.
